        options = {};

      if (!options.inPorts) {
        options.inPorts = {};

      if (options.inPorts instanceof ports.InPorts) {

    Component.prototype.isForwardingInport = function(port) {

    Component.prototype.isForwardingOutport = function(inport, outport) {

    };
